		   <tr><td class="headerrow" colspan="2" class="mform" valign="top" id="forumSubject">Faction questions...<br clear="all" /><script type="text/javascript">document.title = document.title + ": Thread: Faction questions...";</script>
		   <span class="sm">Posted @ Mon, Feb 4th 8:15 AM2002 </span><span class="notbold">| <span class="sm">IP: Logged</span> | <a href="/db/classes.html?class=14&mid=101282478153368&post=1"><a class="sm" href="/db/classes.html?class=14&mid=101282478153368&num=1&post=1&replyto=101282478153368"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." height="11" width="17" /> Reply to this</a></a> | <a class="sm" href="/db/journal2.html?user=49677"><img border="0" src="/shared/user_journal.gif" border="0" height="12" width="17" /> User's Journal</a>   <a name=101282478153368></a></small></td></tr>
		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform" ><span class="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=49677"><span id=Guru>alaaraaf the Puissant</span></a><b><span id=Guru><br>Guru</span></b><br /><img src="/shared/user_star_ico.gif" height="9" width="9" alt="*" /><br />179 posts
		   <br /><nobr><span class="notbold">Score</span>: Excellent [5.00]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=alaaraaf&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>Hey.<br /><br />I have more questions...&nbsp;&nbsp;*Sigh*<br /><br />I have decided that it is long past time I upgraded some of my equipment.  I have had my eye on the cloak and leggings from the <a href="HTTP://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=1287" target="akztarg">Titan samples</a> quest in Erudin for a good long time and have decided it is time I sought these items.  Sadly, I can't afford to just splurge and buy them, <i>(not that I have ever seen them for sale anyhow,)</i> so I'm going to have to quest for them.<br /><br />I have been told I can raise faction by hunting kobolds in the Warrens.  Having spent a little time in the Warrens, I am indeed getting positive faction hits for both Heretics and High Guard of Erudin.  <i>(I'm currently dubious to the guards in Paineel.  A small bonus, but if something goes wrong, it doesn't seem likely they're going to be any help to me, regardless of how much they like me.  *Shrug*)</i><br /><br />I've looked at the bestiary sections for Erudin, Paineel and the Warrens, but haven't been able to find any information pertaining to factions.  <i>(I even posted on the quest page, asking for faction information, but sadly, no-one saw fit to offer me their wisdom.)</i>  From trawling through the strategy posts for Erudin, it seems that each of the casters guilds and the citizens in Erudin have their own faction.  There are various quests which raise factions, but here I have come across a small problem.<br /><br /><li>Is it possible to have good faction in both Erudin and Paineel?  <i>(Small problem.)</i><br />Ideally, I'd like to be able to wander through both cities at will.  However, every quest I have looked at seems to raise one side and lower the other.  If I have to chose, I'll side with the Erudites, for now.  If there is a way to raise both, that'd be ideal.  (After all, then I could do the Paineel Titan sample quest.  I don't want the stick, but I could sell it, after all.)<br /><br /><li>Can I do the quests?<br />It looks like the best quest, will be the kobold molar quest.  <i>(Assuming I can't raise both factions.)</i>  After all, I'm in the Warrens anyhow.  Gathering a heap of molars shouldn't be too difficult.  However, it seems likely that I will still be KoS to all other factions, other than the High Guard.  (Ok, they're all small and I guess I could probably beat them all to death, until they behave...  But that won't get me my cloak, or leggings.  (As satisfying as it might be!))<br /><br />Anyhow, although it seems a little odd to post here, I would appreciate any input you have to offer.  <i>(I could post on the Erudin, or Painell pages, but it's not likely to do me any good.  Hopefully, someone knows what I need to do!  *Grin*)</i><br /><br />Thanks in advance.<br /><br />AlAaraaf.<br /></p><br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br />"Te aurdire no possum. Musa sapienum fixa est in aura."</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td><td align="right" id="fs8" >1 Replies</td></tr></table>
